snippet.title: Green Hell Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Green Hell, from Creepy Jar studio challenges players to survive in the depths of the Amazon rainforest where danger lurks at every turn. Fight off hunger, thirst, disease and enemies unknown. 

Available now in Steam Early Access!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/815370/Green_Hell/
